{"tid":1137894,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛你的人？定你愛的人？","createTime":"2019-05-04T06:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T20:19:16.000Z","uid":98700,"like":194,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8bc15ff4152d4794ca3de1fe26fb52a677bf7699","tid":1137894,"uid":98700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"假設你同兩個人都相愛<br />\n你地會簡一個(a)愛你既人，但你愛佢既程度冇佢愛你咁多<br />\n定係<br />\n你地會簡一個(b)你愛既人，但係你知道佢愛你既程度冇你愛佢咁多<br />\n?<br />\n<br />\n講下自己睇法先 勿屌<br />\n以前我一定會簡一個自己愛既人 那怕佢冇咁鐘意自己 但都係鐘意呀<br />\n但經過好多事之後 發現人都係自私<br />\n咁不如我都自私啲<br />\n簡個愛我既人<br />\n起碼我唔會受傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛你的人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你愛的人"},{"pid":"fbb581509e32aa7cf37319531a4d62f3e8e725fd","tid":1137894,"uid":199692,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"我情願被愛<br />\n<br />\n因為主動追逐好攰，被愛食殘廢餐好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4555fc51863105c1c68d98c17e646c3428048d26","tid":1137894,"uid":177089,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:08:57.000Z","msg":"我揀咗愛我嘅人 因為我愛嘅人唔俾我揀"},{"pid":"2460056bc2e18e90e5d75cad2d8d2b6da8227b0d","tid":1137894,"uid":5273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"無奈要揀愛我的人<br />\n因為我愛的人不愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3613241b43d3d649907ae365f5a9b8d16eb544bb","tid":1137894,"uid":98700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb581509e32aa7cf37319531a4d62f3e8e725fd","tid":1137894,"uid":199692,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"我情願被愛<br />\n<br />\n因為主動追逐好攰，被愛食殘廢餐好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img